Each candle is hand-poured in small batches into a pint sized mason jar in Lancaster, PA. Our vegan dye free soy wax burns at a cooler temperature and slower. This allows an extended clean burn at a slower rate, releasing the captivating scent at a more leisurely pace, and giving the candle a long-lasting experience of up to 84 hours of strong scent throw. Fragrance oils used are cosmetic grade or pure essential oils all phthalate free. Net wax weight 12 ounces.
